i3lock - improved screen locker
===============================
i3lock is a simple screen locker like slock. After starting it, you will
see a white screen (you can configure the color/an image). You can return
to your screen by entering your password.


** That was info from official i3lock located here **

git://code.i3wm.org/i3lock



Changes

added -s for string.

Allows you to set a string to draw on your lock screen such as displaying IP or such.


usage: i3lock -s 'I am a banana'

bugs: still ugly
